name: Pulaw.JS

tagline: MVC Platform for JavaScript. Inspired by Zend Framework
body:
Introducing a Model-View-Controller platform for JavaScript.

Built by [@dunhakdis](https://twitter.com/clubkoncepto) at [@clubkoncepto](http://clubkoncepto.com). This framework helps in building applications rapidly for mobile development.

Bundled Technologies
* [jQuery Mobile](http://jquerymobile.com)
* [Backbone.js](http://backbonejs.org)
* [Underscore.js](http://underscorejs.org)
* [RequireJS](http://requirejs.org)

_Stable Release: 1.0.0 RC-1_ _Changeset: [19854](http://pulaw.codeplex.com/SourceControl/changeset/view/19854)_ _Subversion: [CodePlex](https://pulaw.svn.codeplex.com/svn)_
